parameters:
Excuse me, customer...? The store is already closed...
Please give up and wake up.
I won't give up... I won't give up! This time, I...

Hmm, what should I do...? Manager? There doesn't seem to be
any sign of waking up at all...

Hmm, you're really drunk... Well, I've already contacted
your family, so I'll leave it to them.

Excuse me. It seems like my belongings have caused some
trouble, so I have come to collect them responsibly.

Ugh, it smells like alcohol... I wonder what's good... This
is just...

Oh... quite a small one has come. Can you two carry it by
yourselves?
Yeah, it's totally fine. Let's finish this quickly, Rebecca.
Whoa...!? But, can they really wake up from this...?

Tch...! Such a stubborn person...!! Fine, Rebecca, you take
the legs. I'll take the head.

Yeah, okay... But, you're going to carry the head? Wouldn't
it be better to carry the arms or something?

Hmm, is that so...? The head is the most important part, so
sacrificing the hands and carrying it would be safer, right?

Hmm... When you put it that way, I do feel that way too.
Alright, I'll take the head then. Ready... set... let's go?

H-Hey, hey, stop...! Ugh...!! It's so heavy...!! Why do I
have to go this far for a drunkard...!!
Wow, how cute...! This shop, do you have a cat?
...Meow!? Catch it...!! Please catch that cat!!
Ah, it ran away...! You suddenly shouted so loudly.

W-What's happening!? You two... please catch it!! That cat
has brought the witch's information...!! ...Hurry, run!!
Eh...!? You're suddenly giving me a responsible job...!!
Sigh...!? Why do I have to do something like this!?

That bunny girl's piano... it's the best, right? Especially
the worn silver shine of the black keys... it's even more
dazzling with age...
